<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>400 - Bad Request</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      color: #1e293b;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: #ef4444;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .home-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      background-color: #3b82f6;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background-color 0.2s;
    }

    .home-btn:hover {
      background-color: #2563eb;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>400 - Bad Request</h1>
  <p>Sorry, your request couldn't be understood by the server.</p>
  <a class="home-btn" href="/">Return to Home Page</a>
</body>
</html>
